Summary: Took pictures of climbing rocks and object appeared in picture
divs: sighting details i was at my property in eastern washington, located near the town of malott (on the colville indian reservation) just off of highway 97. in the summer of 2005, i was taking pictures of some climbing cliffs\rocks (i took them because my daughter and i took some classes on rock climbing). i was using a digitrex-2100(digital camera).anyway, i didn't notice anything at the time i was taking the pictures. in my opinion, i wouldn't throw out the idea that it was a bug flying by, but the purple haze appeared in 2 pictures and it sure seems like some sort of object in the air.
